{
  "version": "Notebook/1.0",
  "items": [
    {
      "type": 1,
      "content": {
        "json": "## Log Analytics Usage by Tag\r\n\r\nAfter setting the aggregation `Tag Name` parameter below, results will populate as a table with each resource ID sending logs to Log Analytics and its respective tag value, usage in GB and cost in {Currency}. Some usage may be attributed to an empty resource, which means its logs are not attributable to a specific resource (i.e., do not contain a `_ResourceId` column). You can then export the results to Excel and do further analysis."
      },
      "name": "introText"
    },
    {
      "type": 9,
      "content": {
        "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
        "parameters": [
          {
            "id": "6fda8baa-d8d4-43b6-944e-9581c3338121",
            "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
            "name": "LAWorkspaces",
            "label": "Log Analytics Workspaces",
            "type": 5,
            "isRequired": true,
            "multiSelect": true,
            "quote": "'",
            "delimiter": ",",
            "query": "resources\r\n| where type == 'microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces'\r\n| project id,name\r\n| order by name asc",
            "crossComponentResources": [
              "value::all"
            ],
            "value": [
              "value::all"
            ],
            "typeSettings": {
              "additionalResourceOptions": [
                "value::all"
              ],
              "showDefault": false
            },
            "timeContext": {
              "durationMs": 86400000
            },
            "queryType": 1,
            "resourceType": "microsoft.resourcegraph/resources"
          },
          {
            "id": "73ab229b-2522-4f57-97f8-0f07a5375389",
            "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
            "name": "LATimeRange",
            "label": "Consumption Time Range",
            "type": 4,
            "isRequired": true,
            "value": {
              "durationMs": 86400000
            },
            "typeSettings": {
              "selectableValues": [
                {
                  "durationMs": 86400000
                },
                {
                  "durationMs": 172800000
                },
                {
                  "durationMs": 259200000
                },
